{
  "stem": "12666.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Bismarck has said, Germany doesn't have the resources.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So Hitler didn't kill him, but he demoted him to the command of an army, and he was not punished for disagreeing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we are told, well, the other officers could do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They liked their job too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Plus, there was a secret document called Nacht und Nebel, Night and Fog.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this document was about 50 American and British flyers who were told to escape the prisoner war camp in order to get back on duty.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they escaped several times and they were re-captured and brought back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Himmler, the chief of the Gestapo, said they have to be taught a lesson.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he asked Keitel to sign this document, Night and Fog, by transferring these flyers to Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And these flyers were executed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germany signed the Geneva Convention, so therefore Keitel was-- knew what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was sentencing PWs to their death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Plus, we had PWs, American PWs, in those concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like Ravensbruck and Buchenwald, there were American prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a lieutenant commander of the Navy who said that if I would not have been freed today, I would be dead.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had a whole bunch of dog tags.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These people didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "PWs killed in them, and that is not mentioned, that PWs were killed there, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And 6 million Poles were killed, too, Gypsies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the PWs were killed, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Only-- our PWs were killed, this-- this example.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were even some Navy people too that were transferred to Gestapo and killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was quite emotional to see how people suffered in-- in those concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did conduct human experiments too, and that was horrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
